INSERT INTO
    ais_area (
        mmsi,
        latitude,
        longitude,
        course_over_ground,
        rate_of_turn,
        true_heading,
        speed_over_ground,
        "timestamp",
        altitude,
        distance_to_shore,
        ais_class,
        ais_message_type_id,
        navigation_status_id
    )
SELECT
    *
FROM
    UNNEST(
        $1::INT[],
        $2::DECIMAL[],
        $3::DECIMAL[],
        $4::DECIMAL[],
        $5::DECIMAL[],
        $6::INT[],
        $7::DECIMAL[],
        $8::TIMESTAMPTZ[],
        $9::INT[],
        $10::DECIMAL[],
        $11::VARCHAR[],
        $12::INT[],
        $13::INT[]
    )
ON CONFLICT (mmsi, "timestamp") DO NOTHING
